Measure_ROI_API_v10 参数说明 > 9. measureAndFilterRoi 请求示例

```json
{
  "sessionId": "sess001",
  "workplanId": "wp001",
  "stepId": "step_05_measure_filter_ki67_positive",
  "targetName": "ki67_positive_dapi_roi",
  "operation": "measureAndFilterRoi",
  "inputResources": {
    "parentRoiResourceUuid": "total_dapi_in_islet_roi",
    "measureImageResourceUuid": "ki67_channel.png"
  },
  "params": {
    "measureFeatures": ["MEAN", "AREA", "CIRCULARITY"],
    "filterRules": {
      "MEAN": {"min": 30, "max": 255},
      "AREA": {"min": 0, "max": 1000000000000},
      "CIRCULARITY": {"min": 0, "max": 1}
    }
  },
  "roiRenderParams": {
    "enabled": true,
    "renderImageResourceUuid": "ki67_channel_pseudo.png",
    "renderContour": true,
    "renderMaskOverlay": false,
    "contourColor": "#FFFF00",
    "contourWidthPixels": 2
  },
  "outputOptions": {
    "returnMeasureTable": true,
    "returnMeasureRows": true,
    "returnFilteredRoiZip": true,
    "returnFilteredOutRoiZip": false,
    "returnSummary": true,
    "returnRoiRender": true,
    "returnRenderedImageStoredFile": true,
    "returnRoiMaskStoredFile": true
  }
}
```

Measure_ROI_API_v10 参数说明 > 11. 与 Create_Target 的推荐衔接

`measureAndFilterRoi` 只负责测量、筛选并生成新的 ROI zip。要把筛选后的 ROI 变成 target，应继续调用 `Create_Target_API_v10`：

```json
{
  "sessionId": "sess001",
  "workplanId": "wp001",
  "stepId": "step_06_bind_ki67_positive_dapi_roi",
  "operation": "bindMeasureRoi",
  "sourceType": "measure_roi",
  "sourceMeasureStepId": "step_05_measure_filter_ki67_positive",
  "sourceRoiResourceUuid": "<Measure_ROI 返回的 filteredRoiResourceUuid>",
  "measureTableResourceUuid": "<Measure_ROI 返回的 filteredMeasureTableResourceUuid>",
  "targetName": "ki67_positive_dapi_roi",
  "targetShowName": "Ki67 positive DAPI ROI",
  "measureRoiParams": {
    "operation": "measureAndFilterRoi",
    "inputResources": {
      "parentRoiResourceUuid": "total_dapi_in_islet_roi",
      "measureImageResourceUuid": "ki67_channel.png"
    },
    "params": {
      "measureFeatures": ["MEAN", "AREA", "CIRCULARITY"],
      "filterRules": {
        "MEAN": {"min": 30, "max": 255}
      }
    }
  },
  "roiRenderParams": {
    "enabled": true,
    "renderImageResourceUuid": "ki67_channel_pseudo.png",
    "renderContour": true,
    "contourColor": "#FFFF00",
    "contourWidthPixels": 2
  },
  "outputOptions": {
    "generateDefaultRoiVariants": true
  }
}
```

Create_Target 会把 `roiRenderParams` 和 `measureRoiParams` 一起记录到 target binding 中，供后续 `Get_Target_API_v10` 查询追溯。

Create_Target_API_v10 参数说明 > 10. 请求示例：绑定 Measure_ROI 筛选后的阳性 ROI

```json
{
  "sessionId": "sess001",
  "workplanId": "wp001",
  "stepId": "create_target_ki67_positive",
  "operation": "bindMeasureRoi",
  "sourceType": "measure_roi",
  "sourceMeasureStepId": "measure_filter_ki67_positive",
  "sourceRoiResourceUuid": "ki67_positive_dapi_roi_filtered.zip",
  "measureTableResourceUuid": "ki67_positive_dapi_roi_filtered_measure_table.json",
  "targetName": "ki67PositiveDapiRoi",
  "targetShowName": "Ki67 阳性 DAPI 细胞 ROI",
  "measureRoiParams": {
    "operation": "measureAndFilterRoi",
    "inputResources": {
      "parentRoiResourceUuid": "totalDapiInIsletRoi",
      "measureImageResourceUuid": "ki67_channel.png"
    },
    "params": {
      "measureFeatures": ["MEAN", "AREA", "CIRCULARITY"],
      "filterRules": {
        "MEAN": {"min": 30, "max": 255}
      }
    }
  },
  "roiRenderParams": {
    "enabled": true,
    "renderImageResourceUuid": "ki67_channel_pseudo.png",
    "renderContour": true,
    "contourColor": "#FFFF00",
    "contourWidthPixels": 2
  },
  "outputOptions": {
    "generateDefaultRoiVariants": true
  }
}
```

Create_Target_API_v10 参数说明 > 11. 请求示例：覆盖自动变体策略

```json
{
  "sessionId": "sess001",
  "stepId": "create_target_custom_variants",
  "operation": "bindSegmentRoi",
  "sourceRoiResourceUuid": "segmented_roi.zip",
  "targetName": "tumorRegion",
  "variantStrategy": {
    "boundaryModes": ["in_bound", "on_bound"],
    "offsetLevels": [-0.3, 0, 0.3]
  },
  "outputOptions": {
    "generateDefaultRoiVariants": true
  }
}
```

Create_Target_API_v10 参数说明 > 12. 请求示例：不自动生成 ROI 变体

```json
{
  "sessionId": "sess001",
  "stepId": "create_target_no_variants",
  "operation": "bindSegmentRoi",
  "sourceRoiResourceUuid": "segmented_roi.zip",
  "targetName": "rawCells",
  "outputOptions": {
    "generateDefaultRoiVariants": false
  }
}
```

